'''Stardog One''' was the call sign of a covert [[Alliance Special Forces/Legends|Rebel SpecForce]] operative stationed on [[Level 88]] in the [[Corellian Sector (Nar Shaddaa)/Legends|Corellian Sector]] of the [[Moon/Legends|moon]], [[Nar Shaddaa/Legends|Nar Shaddaa]]. Shortly before the [[Battle of Yavin/Legends|Battle of Yavin]], Rebel operative [[Spane Covis]] called Stardog One warning [[Gender/Legends|him]] of an [[Galactic Empire/Legends|Imperial]] sneak attack on the warehouse district of Level 88.

